### Option 3 (temporary workaround)

Strip the embedded Jackson classes from `SBINEWPG_2023.jar` during the build.

This is ugly, but it works.

For example:

```gradle
tasks.register('cleanSBIJar') {
    doLast {
        copy {
            from(zipTree('libs/SBINEWPG_2023.jar')) {
                exclude 'com/fasterxml/jackson/**'
            }
            into("$buildDir/tmp/sbi")
        }

        ant.jar(
            destfile: "$buildDir/libs/SBINEWPG_2023-fixed.jar",
            basedir: "$buildDir/tmp/sbi"
        )
    }
}
```

Then replace:

```gradle
implementation files('libs/SBINEWPG_2023.jar')
```

with

```gradle
implementation files("$buildDir/libs/SBINEWPG_2023-fixed.jar")
```

